CookObject_0:
(:action CookObject_0
        :parameters (?toolreceptacle - receptacle ?a - agent ?l - location ?o - object)

        :precondition (and 
		(receptacleType ?toolreceptacle StoveBurnerType)
		(atLocation ?a ?l)
		(receptacleAtLocation ?toolreceptacle ?l)
		(holds ?a ?o)
		)
        :effect (and 
		(isHot ?o)
		)
)
